*Iznad* njega je pao veliki kamen (Above him, a large stone fell).

*Iznađ* se nalazio veliki dvorac (Above there was a large castle).

Njegovo ponašanje nije bilo na nivou očekivanom *iznad* njega (His behavior was not up to the expected level above him).

On se šetao *iznad* reke (He was walking above the river).

*Iznad* njegove glave se videlo nebo (Above his head, the sky was visible).

Njegov otac je bio čovek velikih moralnih vrednosti *iznad* svih (His father was a man of great moral values above all).